*@data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name and @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name are spending special time together.* 
 @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name: “I have 5 minutes and I’d like to spend it with you” , @data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name. What would you like to do?”
 @data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name: “I want to play dress-up!”

@data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name: “@data.characters.f2_grandmother.name, it’s for you.”
 @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name: “Thank you, I love this scarf!”
 @data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name: “Wear it, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name!”
